messages.messageBody:
I'm over in the Tri-Cities. My 10yod is also in Girl Scouts. Although I
have reservations about some parts of the program, my dds are currently
enjoying it. Our troop is mulit-age and has 4 leaders, all of whom
homeschool (the leaders that is, half of the kids in the troop go to
school.)

My brother lives in Woodinville. My mom is living in an apartment there
right now, but is getting ready to move back to Gig Harbor.

Mary Ellen
----- Original Message ----- We do live in the
> Seattle area. Bothell, to be exact, which is just north of Woodinville and
> Bellevue.
